{"id":"shocho","term":"Shocho","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>(<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Chronicles 28:18\">2 Chr. 28:18</a>) = Shochoh (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Samuel 17:1\">1 Sam. 17:1</a>) = Shoco (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Chronicles 11:7\">2 Chr. 11:7</a>). See SOCOH.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["2 Chronicles 28:18","1 Samuel 17:1","2 Chronicles 11:7"]}